data.description: Are you ready to move into your next home? It won't take long with this property, vacant and easy to see, the owners are looking for a quick closing so bring your bags.  This immaculate 4/3/2 home in the desirable St James Say goodbye to high electric bills when you own a home with solar electric panels and enjoy next to no electric bills.  The owner states an average electric bill is $50. Newly remodeled bathrooms, cherry wood floors, amazing custom closet, color changing moon lights and tile work are just some of the extras you must see in person to appreciate this upgraded home. Love to entertain?  Patio has a summer kitchen making it perfect for big gatherings. In addition to all the extras have peace of mind since this home comes with a 1 year home warranty.
